WEBVTT

0
00:00:00.119 --> 00:00:03.849
You can personalize a form to control which non-required fields are visible

1
00:00:04.130 --> 00:00:06.110
without affecting what other users see.

2
00:00:06.530 --> 00:00:07.889
To personalize the form,

3
00:00:08.050 --> 00:00:09.789
open the form options menu

4
00:00:09.970 --> 00:00:11.869
and select Personalize Form.

5
00:00:12.250 --> 00:00:12.710
From here,

6
00:00:13.020 --> 00:00:14.529
you can hide fields you don't need.

7
00:00:15.470 --> 00:00:18.430
Required fields are grayed out because they cannot be hidden.

8
00:00:19.250 --> 00:00:21.569
Select update form to apply your changes.

9
00:00:22.700 --> 00:00:25.399
You can return to the default form layout at any time

10
00:00:25.579 --> 00:00:27.760
by reopening the Personalize Form window,

11
00:00:27.979 --> 00:00:29.760
selecting Select All,

12
00:00:29.899 --> 00:00:31.299
and updating the form again.
